eranz-Edikt des Galerius interessieren und mehr als eine Ereignisgeschichte erwarten.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAlte Geschichte. 4aAntikes Rom. 4aLesebuch. 7aHISTORY / Ancient / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Classics and Near East Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110636178oZDB-23-GCN08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  Altertum 2005-2012z9783110345643oZDB-23-OAT0 cprintz978348671716740uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348672898940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486728989423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486728989/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GCNc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OATc2005d2012